{"tid":1460462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請注意,港澳辦陰謀正式開始!","createTime":"2019-08-13T03:05:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T09:15:28.000Z","uid":118951,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7e5fe544dee7d0a5d2cb6069ebfaf10e51f86077","tid":1460462,"uid":118951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:05:48.000Z","msg":"先直接講我個人既推測同觀察：<br />\n中國政府唔止想借spin單野做示威者自己&quot;誤射&quot;，仲想藉此去&quot;証明&quot;:<br />\n示威者有槍&gt;炒作我地想搞恐怖主義&gt;有反恐口實去做D乜<br />\n可能係<strong>武力升級、擴大警權、直接介入</strong>之類<br />\n<br />\n智商正常都可能會駁斥：&quot;唔係警察射唔通示威者射咩&quot;，但我真係見到有好多人覺得真相不明，有可能真係示威者射並且懶有理性咁去分析<br />\n下面我就列下近日既一連串吹既風引導佢地咁思考<br />\n<br />\n港澳辨發言<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZGXC1hX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZGXC1hX.jpg&h=f3e843f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港示威：中國港澳辦稱示威「出現恐怖主義苗頭」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-49316195\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-49316195&d=IX2zbuQlYI18gOdM245y9xSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=d0335e35\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-49316195&h=ea0a13ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-49316195</a><br />\n<br />\n另一方面央視咁樣屈 <br />\n(p.s.央視係好多中國人眼裡比較可信)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dioKGpR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdioKGpR.jpg&h=7dc02239&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而popo方面就扮野話唔知道邊個射<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BMrMakz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBMrMakz.jpg&h=07e6c0bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1065853/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E4%B8%AD%E5%BD%88%E7%9C%BC%E7%90%83%E7%88%86%E8%A3%82-%E8%AD%A6-%E7%84%A1%E8%AD%89%E6%93%9A%E8%88%87%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%9F%B7%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%89%E9%97%9C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1065853%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BD%2588%25E7%259C%25BC%25E7%2590%2583%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%25A3%2582-%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%25AD%2589%25E6%2593%259A%25E8%2588%2587%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%259F%25B7%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%2597%259C&d=IX2zbuQlYI18gOdM245y9xSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=96c38a03\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1065853%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BD%2588%25E7%259C%25BC%25E7%2590%2583%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%25A3%2582-%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%25AD%2589%25E6%2593%259A%25E8%2588%2587%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%259F%25B7%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%2597%259C&h=f3f48ff8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1065853/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E4%B8%AD%E5%BD%88%E7%9C%BC%E7%90%83%E7%88%86%E8%A3%82-%E8%AD%A6-%E7%84%A1%E8%AD%89%E6%93%9A%E8%88%87%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%9F%B7%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%89%E9%97%9C</a><br />\n<br />\n而包括大公文匯話有示威者仿製M320<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=358795&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D358795%26refer%3D&d=IX2zbuQlYI18gOdM245y9xSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=00bb6118\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D358795%26refer%3D&h=2c9ea8dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=358795&amp;refer=</a><br />\n加上tg fb之類都有藍絲同中國人係度傳所謂發射M320既片<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z0RTzFC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz0RTzFC.jpg&h=9949f0ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n煞有介事咁起埋底(有樣有名有姓，唔出哂全部圖)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cetR5NN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcetR5NN.jpg&h=15dde83f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n應該仲有更多更多<br />\n<br />\n呢種其實係媒體同政府好常見既政治技量<br />\n透過抹黑某個群體，其他不明真相既大眾就會覺得問題好嚴重，政府需要處理佢地<br />\n咁政府就能夠為自己既對策同社會控制提供正當理由<br />\n學術上叫做<strong>道德恐慌 (moral panic)</strong><br />\n<br />\n你可能覺得你知我知單眼佬都知，但我相信有好多人未認真去比較過，去FC呢粒真係布袋彈就信左D官媒講法，所以我地要用圖片同真相去反擊，唔好俾D陰謀論成功滲透到大眾，唔係我地做幾多野都會俾人無視。<br />\n<br />\n所以最少要宣傳返個事實畀人知，例如用(好多人眼中仍然)有公信力既媒體例如明報信報去証明<strong>係警察既布袋彈</strong>打傷既:<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/要聞/article/20190813/s00001/1565635190333/眼中彈女子完成緊急手術-未知康復程度\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190813%2Fs00001%2F1565635190333%2F%E7%9C%BC%E4%B8%AD%E5%BD%88%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E6%89%8B%E8%A1%93-%E6%9C%AA%E7%9F%A5%E5%BA%B7%E5%BE%A9%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%A6&d=IX2zbuQlYI18gOdM245y9xSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=63d0d7ca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190813%2Fs00001%2F1565635190333%2F%E7%9C%BC%E4%B8%AD%E5%BD%88%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E6%89%8B%E8%A1%93-%E6%9C%AA%E7%9F%A5%E5%BA%B7%E5%BE%A9%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%A6&h=1b6bd9ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/要聞/article/20190813/s00001/1565635190333/眼中彈女子完成緊急手術-未知康復程度</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tvO6Vhm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtvO6Vhm.jpg&h=261be2d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入面張圖好重要，有明確顯示示威者係俾布袋彈打傷，同埋係可靠既消息來源<br />\n另外我地可比較一下由經濟日報貼既布袋彈:<br />\n<a href=\"https://money.udn.com/money/story/6808/3868725\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoney.udn.com%2Fmoney%2Fstory%2F6808%2F3868725&d=IX2zbuQlYI18gOdM245y9xSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=abcbb42f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://money.udn.com/money/story/6808/3868725</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/toZ9S4f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtoZ9S4f.jpg&h=3def45b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後借一張TG文宣，去破除迷思，先可以防止分化，傳達我地既訴求，Connect埋香港人呢一part先至會贏!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MYQAOeO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMYQAOeO.jpg&h=14029620&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"80f4d826cd7ea39c64b8780ca03b0d2cad1dee42","tid":1460462,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:06:25.000Z","msg":"[總結] 林鄭：818民陣遊行要人呀！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1460414\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1460414</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5a4e7a0ed41539293c4c7d9a0c1aad912644da53","tid":1460462,"uid":132611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:09:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f70546a5fccd43f701f41a97806070ba113939df","tid":1460462,"uid":118951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:09:30.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"8292032c46da790ad1caadcd707d0de3ccb82897","tid":1460462,"uid":93784,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:11:03.000Z","msg":"佢想藉反恐之名，引入新疆模式，將我地屈成為恐怖分子，減少外國干預"},{"pid":"017bb560e1b0bee88795e2a18d8d95ff6e55f1d1","tid":1460462,"uid":38982,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:11:59.000Z","msg":"冇用, 想用恐怖主義苗頭標籤我地既陰謀衰左, 聽下呢個<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ktabZNftdKE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DktabZNftdKE&d=IX2zbuQlYI18gOdM245y9xSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=7e3db52a\"